{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 1 describes the PRISMA flow diagram (Page et al., 2021) of the stages of identification, screening, and inclusion of studies in the meta-analysis.",
    "We used a predesigned spreadsheet in Microsoft Excel to code study details.",
    "Each of the five coders for this phase was randomly assigned to 34 or 35 studies from which to extract data.",
    "Each coder served as the primary or secondary coder for 22 or 23 studies and an adjudicator for 11 or 12 other studies.",
    "Thus, there were three coders assigned to each study, two to conduct independent data extractions and one to adjudicate."
  ]
}